Here are some recent results in this direction in the context of Reeb dynamics; for a more comprehensive overview of the literature, we refer to [

1

] and [

18

]. Hryniewicz–Salomão–Wysocki [

9

] establish sufficient (and 





C


∞




\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
